snippet.title: Kumi Daiko Beatoff 64 homebrew game (all modes gameplay)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Kumi Daiko Beatoff 64 on the N64. This is the runner-up for the 2020 64brew game jam. To find out more and download the ROM, visit N64Squid: https://n64squid.com/kumi-daiko-beatoff-64/(opens in a new tab)

00:00 - Starting gameplay
01:26 - Personal record
03:00 - Strange glitch
03:30 - 2 Player battle
04:28 - 2 Player survival
